headline: Amex Exploration Wins Prestigious Discovery of the Year Award from the Quebec Mineral Exploration Association
summary: Montreal, Quebec--(Newsfile Corp. - October 31, 2025) - Amex Exploration Inc. (TSXV: AMX) (FSE: MX0) (OTCQX: AMXEF) ("Amex" or the "Company") is pleased to announce that it has been awarded the Discovery of the Year by the Quebec Mineral Exploration Association (QMEA) for its outstanding contribution to mineral exploration through the company's exceptional discovery on its Perron Gold Property, located in the Abitibi Greenstone Belt of northwestern Quebec.This prestigious award recognizes a...
